<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Homepage</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .container {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 60px; /* Ensure content is not hidden by the footer */
        }
        header {
            background-color: #005792;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        nav a {
            float: left;
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: auto; /* Push footer to the bottom */
        }
        .about-us {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .about-us h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about-us p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .about-us ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .about-us ul li {
            background: #e0f7fa;
            margin: 5px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #4CAF50;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Home Page</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content about-us">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Empowering Innovation, One Line of Code at a Time</p>
            <p>At wydfaxilDEVSINC, we're a team of passionate software enthusiasts dedicated to crafting cutting-edge solutions that transform the way businesses operate and people live. With a relentless focus on innovation and customer-centricity, we design and develop software that simplifies complexities, drives efficiency, and sparks growth.</p>
            <p>Our story began with a simple yet bold vision: to harness the power of technology to make a meaningful impact. Today, we're proud to be a trusted partner for forward-thinking organizations, helping them navigate the ever-evolving digital landscape with confidence and agility.</p>
            <h3>Our values:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Innovation: We embrace the art of the possible and continuously push the boundaries of what's achievable.</li>
                <li>Collaboration: We believe that together, we can achieve more than the sum of our individual talents.</li>
                <li>Excellence: We strive for exceptional quality in everything we do, from code to customer experience.</li>
                <li>Integrity: We operate with transparency, honesty, and a commitment to doing what's right.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Join us on our mission to shape the future of software and make a difference in the world.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 wydfaxilDEVSINC. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
